original: Linden, Ingegerd (Inga) Maria, tandläkare, Jönköping, f. 2/7/97 i Bollnäs, Gävleb. i., av Birger Stagh o. h. h. f. Skårman. G. 23 m. tandl. David Linden. Barn: Kerstin f. 25, Göran 32. — Stud:ex. i Upps. 15, tandl :-kand. 17, tandläk. 19. Tandl. v. Gbgs folksk. 19-22, v. Jönköp. folksk. sed. 23.
translated: Linden, Ingegerd (Inga) Maria, dentist, Jönköping, b. 2/7/97 in Bollnäs, Gävleborg county, daughter of Birger Stagh and his wife Skårman. Married in 1923 to dentist David Linden. Children: Kerstin, born in 1925, and Göran, born in 1932. Completed high school in Uppsala in 1915, dental studies in 1917, and became a dentist in 1919. Worked as a dentist at Gothenburg elementary school from 1919 to 1922, and at Jönköping elementary school since 1923.
